# libmongoc

This is a prototype for a new MongoDB C library.

These are the tests and examples from the libmongoc distribution 
at https://github.com/chergert/libmongoc

modified by Waitman Gobble <ns@waitman.net> 2013-07-11

This is intended to be used with the FreeBSD ports of devel/libmongoc and
devel/libbson

BSD style Makefile

To build tests, switch to the tests directory and run:

> make

To run the tests:

> make run

To remove the compiled binaries:

> make clean

There is no install.

To build examples, switch to examples directory and run:

> make

To remove the comiled binaries:

> make clean

There is no install.

